moji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係pass冇得book位，咁你本身有冇上網book定？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc8b0e9e1830d67647fe8109d9d08eb657cb241","tid":1031773,"uid":35524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T04:38:49.000Z","msg":"名古屋我真係唔識玩 去9日日本淨係住名古屋個3日覺得浪費左<br />\n除左間酒店好舒服 <br />\n返工時間外其他地方都好似死氣沉沉咁"},{"pid":"24aab1c0c53278d3c321874e11eb3b11cc275b5f","tid":1031773,"uid":139100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T07:06:25.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"8861339c4915a6e3a4e20aac47bd957767c6b023","tid":1031773,"uid":30543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"321803fce6540f77657b852a2b719d80b8d826fa","tid":1031773,"uid":105782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e107b8999eedeb7516eec015c580709879a6e435","tid":1031773,"uid":105782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T03:47:54.000Z","msg":"啱啦有嘢想問，我下個月都會去，請問你有冇買昇龍道巴士pass？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T03:48:41.000Z","msg":"眼殘睇到你有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係pass冇得book位，咁你本身有冇上網book定？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T09:14:50.000Z","msg":"岩岩等上機既時候買左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同時上網book埋聽日去白川鄉既巴士<br />\n一如以往一上機就瞓著左到降落先俾人拍醒<br />\n入境好順暢，跟住諗住去拎3日巴士卷就出事啦<br />\n我問左機場個櫃位佢話要印出黎先換到<br />\n咁我係岩岩去機場嗰陣先買，印唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁是但打算去到名古屋站先換<br />\n上到巴士站條友都係要我印出黎先換得<br />\n然後我就係名古屋站附近轉左成粒鐘都印唔到<br />\n張野有講一定要印出黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EtkTD7G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEtkTD7G.png&h=f88a94dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有野食等陣再講冇印點拎"},{"pid":"8c5292b81076562f1919a4d6b3ad9759437f4e2f","tid":1031773,"uid":30543,"lik