humbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR3760Sj.png&h=969c2f3b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a1dc21a8087fb48a2a0722c348e79e12b05c320","tid":1031773,"uid":139100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T16:20:28.000Z","msg":"牛舌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44f97544210143284b756d3bf3ede8f08d79abb7","tid":1031773,"uid":30543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T02:59:42.000Z","msg":"今日去白川程巴士塞到爆<br />\n九點鐘左右聽到司機話會入呢個點<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RTsF9t4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRTsF9t4.png&h=72720815&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最終我瞓左一教12點先到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去到白川鄉可能要即時上車去高山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ca11e7ceb4a1df1a1af411e16fab526fc51fa1","tid":1031773,"uid":50980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"44f97544210143284b756d3bf3ede8f08d79abb7","tid":1031773,"uid":30543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T02:59:42.000Z","msg":"今日去白川程巴士塞到爆<br />\n九點鐘左右聽到司機話會入呢個點<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RTsF9t4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRTsF9t4.png&h=72720815&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最終我瞓左一教12點先到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去到白川鄉可能要即時上車去高山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T05:27:47.000Z","msg":"4日三夜去一兩個地點咪算  見你之後仲去歧阜   一陣又塞就真係變road trip"},{"pid":"781bc8796ab2acc14ee82d4541fd379d863316ae","tid":1031773,"uid":30543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46ca11e7ceb4a1df1a1af411e16fab526fc51fa1","tid":1031773,"uid":50980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"44f97544210143284b756d3bf3ede8f08d79abb7","tid":1031773,"uid":30543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T02: