e":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T11:02:04.000Z","msg":"係白川鄉搖左一粒鐘車就到高山<br />\n入黑之後條街真係好L凍<br />\n酒店放低左野本身打算食味藏天國/丸明<br />\n點知兩間都話full左 巴打想食就得book位<br />\n出面得2度行左成半粒鐘都冇得食<br />\n打開google 揀左間叫Yamatake Shoten<br />\n間野入到有個大雪櫃 然後就叫你揀肉<br />\n每塊都差唔多1500g左右 同佢講可以要1半都得<br />\n咁我行到嬲嬲地直接要左塊1400g既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個老世確認左兩次之後切左<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gtQP5qQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgtQP5qQ.png&h=949029c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9nsu5r8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9nsu5r8.png&h=03b0968e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外佢有d蔥同南瓜之類仲有甜品可以任食<br />\n如果識日本呢間個老世幾好吹<br />\n又話黎過香港,又話佢d牛點樣返黎<br />\n仲不停用普通話問檯鬼佬好唔好食（佢淨係識問「好吃？）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過1-2個人黎淨係可以坐他他咪位<br />\n我燒到一半就腳痺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e185ef3fc621706bd817eaf9795204fc9a5cb66e","tid":1031773,"uid":30543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95422558cf0f3323c1298dd228c262ca998540ac","tid":1031773,"uid":105782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5589857508273cecccfea1e592951cac272ae32","tid":1031773,"uid":30543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"309a0b9bbcfb678a81652de9050cd33772b0dbc2","tid":1031773,"uid":105782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T08:24:01.000Z","msg":"<strong>因為之前爬過文話，pass<br />\n唔接受預約<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T10:33:01.000Z","msg":"放心個呀姐冇留難過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T10:43:24.000Z","msg":"<strong>ok另外想問多樣野，個pass係咪包機場來回車飛？如果有，一用張車飛係咪已經開通埋個pass？因為我頭兩三日都會喺名古屋，之後先上高山白川鄉<br />\n<br />\nanyway謝謝解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/